            "heading": "The strength within",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_7LNJ7A": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Mānuka honey isn't just powerful because of where it comes from-but because of what's inside. Each drop contains over 200 naturally occurring compounds-amino acids, antioxidants, enzymes, and bioactives like methylglyoxal (MGO) and hydrogen peroxide-working together to support the body's healing process. These components help create an environment where wounds can recover more quickly, bacteria is kept in check, and the skin is supported at every stage. Studies show medical-grade Manuka honey is effective against antibiotic-resistant bacteria such as staph, MRSA, and pseudomonas, making it a safe, trusted option in modern wound care.<br/><br/></p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
