        "text_cWKXBw": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We design our packaging to do less harm and more good. Whenever possible, we use recycled, recyclable, refillable, or biodegradable materials. First Honey products are packaged in glass or post-consumer recycled resin (PCR), and our unit cartons are made from FSC-certified recycled paper. Because how we package healing should reflect the care we put into what's inside.</p>",
